WWW-Twittervision version 0.01
==============================

Perl extension to the Twittervision API.
Also contains a simple parser to extract locations from
a tweet, as specified on http://twittervision.com/api.html

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  blah blah blah

